<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$huo-zhen-bu-lu-zi-lao-ye" href="/people/huo-zhen-bu-lu-zi-lao-ye">霍真布鲁兹老爷</a>，<strong title="http://www.jianshu.com/p/4d1bdf5a5611" class="zu-question-my-bio"><a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/4d1bdf5a5611" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">jianshu.com/p/4d1bdf5a5</span><span class="invisible">611</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a></strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="313">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$axeav-joshua" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/axeav-joshua" class="zg-link" title="呐喊的达瓦里希">呐喊的达瓦里希</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$Yangtze-River" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/Yangtze-River" class="zg-link" title="武长江">武长江</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


